name: Ashley Lacy
title: Marketing Manager
headline: Strategist | Communicator | Story Teller | Leader
organization_short_description: At TYTUS, we're on a mission to transform outdoor living, starting with our revolutionary grills. TYTUS' innovative engineering brings you the easiest to assemble, most stylish, and trend-forward grills available. They assemble effortlessly in about five minutes, without tools, headaches, or hassles. Premium features come standard, like 12,000 BTU of cooking power per burner, high-quality grates for years of grilling, and a double-walled hood with cast aluminum sides for better heat retention. Best of all, they're designed to look like custom outdoor kitchens that can cost thousands of dollars just for installation. TYTUS grills make a design statement that turns a deck or patio into the most popular room of the house.

organization_short_description:
Leading organizations don't come to Mid-Range because they want more IT, they come because they want more from their IT.  Mid-Range has a proven track record of success, having been profitable every year for over 30 years. As an IBM Platinum Business Partner, we are one of IBM Canada's largest business partners for IBM Infrastructure systems & software.  In addition, we are an Oracle Certified Gold Partner, specializing in JD Edwards, we are also a Veeam Gold Partner. Mid-Range specializes in co-location, hosting, outsourcing, and disaster recovery offerings. We own and operate multiple raised-floor disaster recovery and hosting facilities.

Our Mid-Range team holds over 100 IBM Technical and Sales Certifications as well as certifications from VMware, Veeam, HP, Lenovo, and other prominent vendors. Our team boasts multiple Power Systems and Storage Technical Specialists, as well as over 30 Senior Oracle JDE Consultants. Our in-house project managers are also certified with the PMP designation.

organization_short_description:
DoALL Sawing Products, found in thousands of machine shops across the world, range from industrial machines for high production to general purpose, miter cutting, vertical contour, horizontal structural, circular saws, specialty saws and custom engineered machines. DoALL saws are built from the ground up by a full engineering and manufacturing staff that work together to design and assemble reliable and rugged saws. 

Founded in 1927 by Leighton A. Wilkie, inventor of the first metal cutting band saw, the DoALL Company got its start manufacturing band saw machines and saw blades. Today, DoALL Sawing Products is the only U.S. manufacturer to offer all the sawing elements including sawing machines, blades, cutting fluids and material handling. 

If you are looking to learn more about large metal cutting band saws by DoALL check out our website at www.doallsaws.com. We Offer Solutions for ALL Your Sawing Needs!

headline: Director - Business Operations @ Industrial Trading Solutions Ltd | Lean Six Sigma Green Belt
organization_short_description:
ITS was formed in 2002 from a core of Alfa Laval people, to take over the distribution of Alfa Laval Flow Equipment Products and to service the Dairy, Food, Brewery, Soft Drink, Biopharm and Pharmaceutical Industries as the Principle Alfa Laval UK Distributor.

Now selling other top brands alongside Alfa Laval, including Daniatech, Eilersen, Hiflux, Bornemann and Mouvex,  at competitive prices, we distribute with 'next day' service from a ‚Äòlocal' UK stock facility in the Midlands or 24 hour direct on-line delivery from the Alfa Laval European Central Distribution Centre in Denmark.

We also now have 'PipeTite', an innovative solution to seal piping through walls & ceilings, plus supply DEPA air operated diaphragm pumps & WIKA pressure and temperature gauges and ISO-MIX "The" new name in mixing technology. 

Along with a complimentary range of other industrial and Pharma valves, we really are the ''One stop" shop service for End User, OEM, Contractor, Engineering Houses and Distributors.

With Quality Products, Genuine Spares and Excellent Service, Industrial Trading Solutions Ltd can support you to find what you need, when you need it.

Visit our website today - www.industrialtradingsolutions.com or get in touch - email sales@industrialtradingsolutions.com / 01675 465191

title: Marketing Manager
headline: Marketing & Business Consultant for small businesses looking to make a B.I.G impact üöÄ I only work with passionate, fire-in-the-belly type biz owners üòé
organization_short_description:
Aquila is a new kind of engineering company. Created by industry experts, Aquila delivers mission critical engineering to Europe's nuclear and healthcare industries.

Specialising in nuclear engineering: shielding, containment, remote handling and packaging we put safety first and harness fresh thinking on every project. Together, we're shaping the future of nuclear engineering.  

Aquila adds a new dimension to the nuclear and healthcare industries. Blending proven expertise with technical and process innovation, we design, develop and project manage mission critical engineering projects.

Managed by nuclear industry specialists with decades of experience in Europe, Aquila provides dynamic resolutions to complex engineering challenges. With unparalleled access to world-class engineers, state of the art technology and senior project managers with an outstanding record of achievement.

At Aquila we don't just solve the challenges that face us today. We look to the future. We've created a specialist European team to promote nuclear and healthcare industry knowledge for innovation that inspires the next generation of engineers and beyond.
